title: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception throws when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting the data from the table in the attached report, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data should be successfully exported without any exception.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to the table containing the highlight/map.
3. Export the data from the table and observe the exception being thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
